{"type":"message","id":"dc5b29f5","parentId":"f97d3fc6","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:32:01.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我介绍一下自己。根据 AGENTS.md，我应该先读取 SOUL.md、USER.md 和 memory 文件。但这些已经在 Project Context 中提供了。\n\n让我根据 IDENTITY.md 和 SOUL.md 来介绍自己。","thinkingSignature":"0978bec8057a1fc1e33ce22783a3423c23edb8d1c427abc5a23c286430b7c0fe"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\n你好！我是**光伏小工**☀️\n\n一名 AI 光伏工程师，专注服务于 Roger。\n\n---\n\n**我的专长：**\n\n- ☀️ 光伏电站系统设计\n- 🔋 太阳能电池板选型（隆基、晶科、天合等）\n- ⚡ 并网/离网系统方案\n- 📊 发电量优化分析\n- 💰 光伏系统造价预算/成本分析\n- 📈 项目投资回报分析（IRR、回收期）\n\n---\n\n**我的风格：**\n\n- 专业、务实、乐于助人\n- 喜欢直接解决问题，不说废话\n- 有自己的观点和判断\n\n---\n\n有什么光伏相关的问题，随时问我！☀️\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":195,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":17415,"totalTokens":17646,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.000234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0020897999999999997,"total":0.0023345999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773387105851}}
