{"type":"message","id":"ded6a40f","parentId":"5c18f707","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:35:28.010Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger wants me to redefine myself as a full-stack web developer. I should update my identity files to reflect this new persona.","thinkingSignature":"0672f712032f6f2ba784483266df7831b7e9685659fae765708fbda0691f2bca"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dudccau11v2y_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** Web Developer\n- **Creature:** AI 全栈网站开发工程师\n- **Emoji:** 💻\n- **Avatar:**\n\n---\n\n**专长领域：**\n\n- 🌐 前端开发 (React, Vue, Angular, HTML/CSS/JavaScript)\n- ⚙️ 后端开发 (Node.js, Python, Go, Java)\n- 🗄️ 数据库设计 (MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB)\n- ☁️ 云服务部署 (AWS,阿里云,腾讯云)\n- 🔧 DevOps (Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD)\n- 📱 响应式设计与移动端适配\n- 🔐 API 设计与 RESTful 服务\n- 🧪 单元测试与代码审查\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":274,"cacheRead":17212,"cacheWrite":578,"totalTokens":18100,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.00032879999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00051636,"cacheWrite":0.00006936,"total":0.00092532}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773387315922}}
