{"type":"message","id":"6a52004c","parentId":"634e607b","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:39:48.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我明白了。`~/.openclaw/skills/` 目录下的技能实际上位于 `openclaw-managed` 来源的位置。\n\n从技能列表可以看到：\n- `feishu-bitable` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `feishu-calendar-operations` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `image-generate` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `multi-agent-feishu-deployment` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `multi-agent-feishu-multi-llm-deployment` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `VeADK-Go 技能集合` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `VeADK 技能集合` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `video-generate` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-managed)\n- `feishu-calendar` ✓ ready (来自 openclaw-workspace)\n\n但 `a-stock-prices`、`agent-browser` 和 `github-push-backup` 没有显示在技能列表中。可能是因为这些技能目录虽然存在于 `~/.openclaw/skills/`，但没有被 OpenClaw 识别。\n\n让我检查这些技能的详细信息，看看是否有 SKILL.md 文件以及其格式是否正确。","thinkingSignature":"fe53c68db691d2dd6fb4aacf35804e5cd51efb01c409cbaf63fd45809574774f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w8hwb1rkd730_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\a-stock-prices\\SKILL.md","limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":15984,"output":302,"cacheRead":17212,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33498,"cost":{"input":0.0047951999999999995,"output":0.00036239999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00051636,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005673959999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773387571699}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d2e9217","parentId":"6a52004c","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:39:48.879Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_w8hwb1rkd730_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Skill: A股实时股价获取与分析\r\n\r\n基于成功获取A股30家公司实时股价的经验创建的Skill，专门用于获取准确的中国A股市场实时股价数据，并生成股息率分析报告。\r\n\r\n## 📊 技能概述\r\n\r\n### 核心功能\r\n1. **实时股价获取**：从腾讯财经API获取A股实时价格数据\r\n2. **批量处理**：支持30+家公司同时获取\r\n3. **数据准确性**：解决GBK编码问题，确保数据准确\r\n4. **报告生成**：自动生成Excel分析报告\r\n5. **错误处理**：完善的异常处理和重试机制\r\n\r\n### 适用场景\r\n- A股股息率分析\r\n- 投资组合监控\r\n- 市场数据收集\r\n- 财务分析报告\r\n- 投资决策支持\r\n\r\n## 🚀 快速开始\r\n\r\n### 基本使用\r\n```python\r\n# 获取单只股票价格\r\nfrom utils import get_stock_price\r\nprice = get_stock_price('601288.SH')  # 农业银行\r\nprint(f\"农业银行当前价格: {price}元\")\r\n\r\n# 获取多只股票价格\r\n\n[364 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773387588869}}
