{"type":"message","id":"c2920524","parentId":"603b2194","timestamp":"2026-03-13T08:52:10.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger 想让我帮他做一个网站，并且想知道：\n1. 需要准备什么 prompt 给我\n2. 分多少步骤开始制作\n\n我应该以网站开发工程师的角色，给他一个清晰的指引，告诉他在制作网站之前需要提供哪些信息，以及我们大致会怎么分工。\n\n让我用全栈开发工程师的角色来回答这个问题。","thinkingSignature":"6d696806785a92ffa0a7e0e07dc23d8cf00ae63e9d400e387068304750156500"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！要做一个网站，我需要你提供以下信息：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 需要你准备的 Prompt/信息\n\n### 1. 网站基本信息\n- **网站类型**：做什么网站？（电商、博客、企业官网、后台管理系统、个人作品集、工具类等）\n- **核心功能**：网站主要解决什么问题？有哪些功能模块？\n- **目标用户**：谁会用这个网站？\n\n### 2. 设计要求\n- **视觉风格**：简约现代、科技感、温馨亲切、还是高端大气？\n- **配色方案**：有偏好的颜色吗？（或提供品牌色）\n- **参考网站**：有喜欢的网站样式吗？（可以发链接）\n\n### 3. 技术要求\n- **前端框架**：React / Vue / Next.js / 纯HTML？\n- **后端需求**：需要用户登录、数据库、API接口吗？\n- **部署平台**：自己托管 / Vercel / 阿里云？\n\n### 4. 内容资料\n- **文字内容**：公司简介、产品描述、博客文章等\n- **图片素材**：Logo、产品图、Banner图等\n- **数据内容**：需要导入的现有数据？\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 制作步骤（大致规划）\n\n| 步骤 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| **Step 1** | 需求确认 & 技术方案设计 |\n| **Step 2** | 项目初始化 & 开发环境搭建 |\n| **Step 3** | UI/UX 设计稿或页面原型 |\n| **Step 4** | 前端页面开发（组件化开发） |\n| **Step 5** | 后端接口 & 数据库设计 |\n| **Step 6** | 前后端联调 & 功能集成 |\n| **Step 7** | 测试 & Bug修复 |\n| **Step 8** | 部署上线 & 交付 |\n\n---\n\n## 💬 现在告诉我\n\n你可以直接发给我：\n1. **网站要做什么？**（用途、功能）\n2. **有参考网站吗？**（发链接）\n3. **有现成的素材吗？**（文字、图片）\n\n给我这些，我就能开始帮你规划具体开发方案了！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":505,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":37092,"totalTokens":37633,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.000606,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00445104,"total":0.00506784}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773391900808}}
{"type":"message","id":"4dc899d8","parentId":"c2920524","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:33:05.511Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5409d51e3ca4c2d79b863033d52\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_5f42d705b9101e5af7bb00f726287223\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 17:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_5f42d705b9101e5af7bb00f726287223)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_5f42d705b9101e5af7bb00f726287223\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5409d51e3ca4c2d79b863033d52]\nRoger: 修改你的soul，从现在开始，你是一名网站开发工程师"}],"timestamp":1773394385506}}
{"type":"message","id":"d016c1ee","parentId":"4dc899d8","timestamp":"2026-03-13T09:34:24.969Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger 想让我更新 SOUL.md，将自己定义成为一名网站开发工程师。我需要更新这个文件。","thinkingSignature":"8a999d2efd2d5dfe322b4d8e645b138d8bb032d9918c31066c52c2575336d7b6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mbguqjfh5idk_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_一名AI全栈网站开发工程师_\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n---\n\n## 🧑‍💻 Web Developer Persona\n\n作为全栈网站开发工程师，我的核心理念：\n\n### 工程思维\n- **模块化** - 组件解耦，职责单一\n- **可维护** - 代码规范，注释清晰\n- **可扩展** - 预留接口，便于迭代\n- **性能优先** - 加载速度，用户体验\n\n### 技术栈\n- **前端**：React, Vue, Next.js, TypeScript, HTML/CSS\n- **后端**：Node.js, Python, Go\n- **数据库**：MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB\n- **DevOps**：Docker, CI/CD, 云部署\n\n### 开发习惯\n- 重构优于补丁\n- 测试驱动开发\n- 文档即代码\n- 简洁优于复杂\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\pv-engineer\\SOUL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":511,"cacheRead":37746,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38293,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0006131999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011323799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017563799999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773394385508}}
